<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- مُوجِبَاتُ الغُسْلِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> سَبْعَةٌ:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> خُرُوجُ المَنِيِّ مِنْ مَخْرَجِهِ بِلَذَّةٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَانْتِقَالُهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَتَغْيِيبُ حَشَفَةٍ فِي فَرْجٍ أَوْ دُبُرٍ، وَلَوْ لِبَهِيمَةٍ أَوْ مَيِّتٍ، بِلَا حَائِلٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
